{
  "texts": [
    "Next, we collect additional automatically annotated training cases.",
    "Automatic annotation.",
    "To further enrich our dataset, we used a simple heuristic to collect noisily-labeled instances.",
    "We began by selecting papers with statement titles that followed specific Part-Of-Speech (POS) tagging structures (NP-(VBP/VBZ)) based on the Stanford POS tagging scheme 35.",
    "We then transformed the statement titles into questions by employing a simple method, which involved inserting copulas like 'is' or auxiliary verbs such as 'does' at the beginning of the sentence."
  ]
}